The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 06 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this Sunday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks about Obama's plan to bankrupt the coal industry and the EPA effort to block power plants from being built that would be able to handle extra demand during the winter. On Friday, the White House attacked a Prison Planet.com article posted earlier in the week on the controversial topic.
